sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Browser: Click bell icon (bottom-left corner)
    Browser->>Browser: navigator.serviceWorker.register(sw.js)
    Browser->>Browser: pushManager.subscribe(vapidPublicKey)
    Browser->>API: POST /api/notification
    Note right of Browser: { endpoint, keys: { p256dh, auth } }
    API->>DB: Notification.upsert(userId, endpoint, p256dh, auth)
    DB-->>API: Subscription saved
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
    Browser-->>User: Subscribed to push notifications
